Kim-ku3: Gi7-lang5 e5 ki5-to2, i e5 lek8-liong7 u7 toa7 kong-hau7. (Nga2-kok 5: 16)
Ti7 1600 ni5 cheng5 A-hui-li7-ka e5 sou2-chai7 chit8-ui7 keng3-khian5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3 choe3 Mou5-ni-ka, i u7 chit8 e5 hau7-senn kio3 choe3 Ou3-kou2-su7-teng, i se3-han3 e5 si5 lau7-pe7 chiu7 si2 khi3. Lau7-bu2 chit8-si3-lang5 chiu2 i, lau7-bu2 it-seng e5 ki5-to2 si7 ai3 kiann2 choe3 chit8 e5 ho2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, na7-si7 kiann2 khiok bo5 ai3 chiau3 lau7-bu2 e5 ki5-thai7, ai3 se3-kan khah koe3-thau5 ti7 to7-li2, au7-lai5 khi3 kau3 Lo5-ma2 liu5-hak8 e5 si5, oan5-choan5 li7-khui to7-li2 soa3 kiann5 ti7 ou-am3 e5 lou7. Chong2-si7 lau7-bu2 toa3 ti7 kou3-hiong me5-jit8 to ui7-tioh8 i e5 kiann2 piann3-mia7 e5 ki5-to2 ai3 i hoe2-kai2, lau7-bu2 mui2-jit8 to lau5 bak8-sai2 tui3 Chu2 kiu5, tioh8 hou7 i e5 kiann2 hoan2-hoe2, u7 chit8 pai2 u7 chiong kiann2 e5 su7 ka7 chit e5 sian-sinn kong2 e5 si5, sian-sinn an2-ni an-ui3 i kong2 ¡§Chhiann2 li2 an-sim tng2-khi3, Siong7-te3 it-teng7 e7 pang-chan7 li2, chhin-chhiunn7 li2 chit-khoan2 piann3-mia7 e5 ki5-to2, li2 e5 kiann2 tek-khak boe7 biat8-bo5.¡¨
Ko2-jian5 si7 lah, u7 chit8-jit8 Ou2-kou2-su-teng ti7 hoe-hng5 teh san3-pou7 khoann3 hoe e5 si5, hut-jian5 u7 thiann-tioh8 chit8 e5 siann tui3 teng2-bin7 lai5 ka7 i kong2 ¡§Theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8, theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8¡¨. I chhek tioh8 sim chiu7 jip8-khi3 thak8 chheh-pang5 theh8 chit8-pun2 ku2-ku2 bo5 teh thak8 e5 Seng3-keng hian-khui chit8-e7 khoann3 hit chat Seng3-keng chiu7-si7 Lo5-ma2 13 chiunn 13-14 chat. ¡§Sou2 kiann5 tioh8 toan-chiann3, chhin-chhiunn7 ti7 jit8-si5, boh8-tit hounn3-sek sia5-im5, boh8-tit sann-chinn oan3-tou3. Tioh8 chheng Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, boh8-tit ui7-tioh8 jiok8-the2 tou5-bou5, ti3-kau3 than3 su-iok8.¡¨
Chit e5 si5-chun7 Ou2-kou2-su-teng, leng5-hun5 chhenn2 khi2-lai5 siunn7 tioh8 lau7-bu2, siunn7 tioh8 Siong7-te3. Tng2-khi3 kou3-hiong chhoe7 lau7-bu2 jin7-choe7, ia7 kong2 chit e5 keng-koe3. Lau7-bu2 chin-chiann3 kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3, in-ui7 kiann2 thiann-tioh8 ¡§theh8 khi2-lai5 thak8¡¨ hit e5 siann e5 si5 tu2-tu2 i e5 ma-ma ti7 chhu3-nih8 ui7-tioh8 i teh ki5-to2, au7-lai5 Ou2-kou2-su-teng chiu7 chiann5-choe3 kau3-hoe7 chin chhut-mia5 e5 lang5, lang5 ia7 chheng i choe3 Seng3 Ou2-kou2-su-teng, i u7 kong2 ¡§goa2 bo5 ti3-kau3 biat8-bo5, oan5-choan5 si7 tui3 goa2 e5 lau7-bu2 mi5-jit8 piann3-mia7 ki5-to2 e5 kong-lo5. Gi7-lang5 e5 ki5-to2, i e5 lek8-liong7 u7 toa7 kong-hau7. (I. L. Chhi5)
